{"tid":1224267,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"添馬公園103萬遍六字大明咒念誦","createTime":"2019-06-15T02:44:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T13:22:12.000Z","uid":142708,"like":53,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"078a50dbf124bc7c7eec86ff956932036fcff470","tid":1224267,"uid":142708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:44:56.000Z","msg":"*103萬遍六字大明咒念誦*<br />\n*六字大明咒*<br />\n漢文拼音：唵嘛呢叭咪吽<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">拉丁拼音：Om mani padme hum</span></span><br />\n原為梵文，為佛教其中一個最重要的咒語。其中有很深的寓意。大概是：以修持菩提心及空性見來去除自我的傲慢心、嫉妒心、貪欲、愚痴、吝嗇心、瞋恚心及去除各種痛苦。<br />\n<br />\n為感謝6月9日為香港走到街頭的103萬人，也希望能把這103萬人的願望連結一起，我們一群佛友，發心持誦103萬次六字大明咒，迴向給香港人出力的103萬人平安健康，祈願所有香港人生活幸福。<br />\n<br />\n開始時間：6月15日下午4:00完結時間：至合共完成103萬次念誦為止<br />\n地點：添馬公園<br />\n*歡迎各位加入"},{"pid":"30a9d0890dc43c49f15848ccd0f930b4aa543047","tid":1224267,"uid":142708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:45:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c068e5069597b273af43c8260c0db05731a5862","tid":1224267,"uid":142708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:45:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"edc015dfbc980a07963d4f47bba8fe4bdc708acd","tid":1224267,"uid":142708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:45:53.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"9c8271b7ea5317a8295102874e736d05ea4c3cbc","tid":1224267,"uid":142708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:46:15.000Z","msg":"佛都有火啦今舖"},{"pid":"d8dbd2d2659311ae066540801867d3889e54ff1e","tid":1224267,"uid":129013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:46:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7fc8dfed96c789873e0d2536cd8d8fff9c4c75ff","tid":1224267,"uid":179824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:47:12.000Z","msg":"真係佛都有火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.g